<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00409/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一只拳套，戴上后使用者只能使出<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/left-punch/">左勾拳</a>以对敌<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>██市██仓库<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>收藏在Site-CN-81低价值物品柜中<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong>这个东西除了能打出连续普通拳以外还有什么作用？——Dr.阙</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00409" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00409" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00409-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zeta-9-beta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6441401); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6441401&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222217" alt="zeta-9-beta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6441401)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zeta-9-beta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6441401); return false;">zeta-9-beta</a></span></p>
