<p><span id="u-credit-00382" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00382" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00382-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nanxia" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5981934); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5981934&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222217" alt="nanxia" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5981934)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nanxia" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5981934); return false;">nanxia</a></span></p>
